'''Porn groove'''{{citation needed|date=September 2018}} is the music [[soundtrack]] to typical [[Pornographic movie|pornographic films]], or a [[Music genre|genre]] of music that imitates such music. The [[electric guitar]] with [[wah-wah pedal]] is the most common instrument associated with porn groove, and synonymous with the genre. Simple, often [[minimalist music|minimalistic]]-sounding drums, with the [[rimshot]] sound being commonly associated with porn groove.{{citation needed|date=September 2018}} In some movies such as the popular and influential ''[[Deep Throat (film)|Deep Throat]]'', the film is cut with the music in mind, making the thrust in the scenes flow with the music.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fusedmagazine.com/Past_Issues/Issue_22/Deep_Throat.aspx |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080105051415/http://www.fusedmagazine.com/Past_Issues/Issue_22/Deep_Throat.aspx |archivedate=2008-01-05 |title=Archive - ''Deep Throat'' |work=[[Fused Magazine]] |quote=Gerard Damiano edited the film to its music, so the actions would match and the beat would match…like up and down strokes on the old shaft…it was pretty clever.}}</ref>

