{{Infobox television | show_name = The Switch Drag Race | image = The-switch-desafio-mundial.png | caption = Promotional logo for Season 2 of ''The Switch'' | genre = [[Reality television#Reality competition/game shows|Reality competition]] | based_on = ''[[RuPaul's Drag Race]]'' | director = Ricardo Durán<ref>{{cite|url=http://www.cooperativa.cl/noticias/entretencion/television/mega/director-de-the-switch-queremos-dignificar-el-oficio-del-transformista/2015-08-26/000841.html|title=Director of "The Switch": We Want to Dignify the Art of Female Impersonation|author=Ma Fca.. Maldonado|date=August 26, 2015|journal=Cooperativa.cl. ''(Article in Spanish. Title translated to English)''}}</ref> | host = [[:es:Karla Constant|Karla Constant]] | judges = {{Plainlist| * Nicole Gaultier (Season 1 and 2) * [[Íngrid Cruz]] (Season 1 and 2) * Juan Pablo González (Season 1) * Sebastián Errázuriz (Season 1) * [[:es:Oscar Mediavilla|Oscar Mediavilla]] (Season 2)
